<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="faqs-container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-heading">Properties - <b>Properties Related</b></div>
        <div class="faq-content">
            <br>
            <b>Q1: How can I search for properties based on specific criteria?</b>
            <br>
            <p>You can use our advanced search filters to narrow down your options based on location, budget, property type (e.g., apartments, villas, commercial spaces), and amenities such as parking, swimming pools, or furnished options.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q2: What types of properties are available on the platform?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Our platform offers a diverse range of properties, including:
            <ul>
                <li>Residential properties: Apartments, villas, townhouses.</li>
                <li>Commercial spaces: Offices, retail spaces, warehouses.</li>
                <li>Land plots for development.</li>
            </ul>
            </p>
            <br>
            <b>Q3: Can I contact the property owner or agent directly?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Yes, each property listing includes contact details for the owner or agent. You can reach out to them directly via the provided phone number, email, or inquiry form.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q4: Are there verified listings for properties?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Yes, we prioritize verified listings to ensure accuracy and trust. Verified listings are clearly marked, providing you with confidence in your property search.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q5: What are the benefits of creating a user account for property searches?</b>
            <br>
            <p>By creating an account, you can:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Save your favorite properties.</li>
                <li>Receive notifications for new listings that match your criteria.</li>
                <li>Access personalized recommendations.</li>
                <li>Easily manage your inquiries and preferences.</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <b>Q6: Is there assistance available for first-time buyers or renters?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Absolutely! We offer guides and tips for first-time buyers or renters, as well as the option to connect with real estate experts who can guide you through the process.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-heading">Make an Inquiry - <b>Inquries Related</b></div>
        <div class="faq-content">
            <br>
            <b>Q1: How can I submit an inquiry for a property?</b>
            <br>
            <p>To submit an inquiry, navigate to the property listing of your choice and fill out the inquiry form with your name, contact details, and message. Click “Submit” to connect with the property owner or agent.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q2: What personal details are required to connect with a landlord or vendor?</b>
            <br>
            <p>We typically require your full name, phone number, email address, and any specific details related to your inquiry to ensure smooth communication.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q3: Is my data secure after submitting an inquiry?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Yes, your personal information is protected through robust encryption measures. We comply with data privacy laws to ensure your data is secure.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q4: How soon can I expect a response after making an inquiry?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Responses are usually received within 24-48 hours, depending on the availability of the landlord or vendor.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q5: Can I inquire about multiple services at once (e.g., property and home shifting)?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Yes, our platform allows you to submit inquiries for multiple services. Simply choose the relevant categories and provide details in your inquiry.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q6: Are the vendors verified and reliable?</b>
            <br>
            <p>We carefully vet our vendors for credibility and reliability. Verified vendors are clearly marked to ensure quality service.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-heading">Partners - <b>Partners Related</b></div>
        <div class="faq-content">
            <br>
            <b>Q1: How can builders and developers list their properties on the website?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Builders and developers or Vendors can register. Once approved, they can upload property listings with details, photos, and pricing.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q2: What benefits do vendors gain from partnering with the platform</b>
            <br>
            <p>Vendors can:
            <ul>
                <li>Reach a larger audience.</li>
                <li>Showcase their services and portfolio.</li>
                <li>Gain leads directly from interested customers.</li>
            </ul>
            </p>
            <br>
            <b>Are there any fees or commissions for partners?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Yes, we charge a nominal fee or commission depending on the type of partnership and services availed. Contact our team for detailed pricing plans.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q4: How are partners verified for credibility and quality assurance?</b>
            <br>
            <p>We conduct a thorough verification process that includes background checks, service reviews, and documentation to ensure credibility and quality.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q5: How can partners manage their listings or profiles on the platform?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Partners can log in to their dedicated dashboard to update listings, respond to inquiries, and track performance metrics.</p>
            <br>
            <b>Q6: Are there analytics or tools available for partners to track customer interactions?</b>
            <br>
            <p>Yes, we provide analytics tools that offer insights into customer views, inquiries, and engagement trends to help partners optimize their offerings.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-heading">General Inquiries - <b>General & Account Related</b></div>
        <div class="faq-content">
            <br>
            <b>Q: How can I contact OfferNMove for any queries or support?</b>
            <br>
            <p>You can reach out to us anytime at <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=info@offernmove.com&su=Support%20Request&body=Hello%20Team," target="_blank">info@offernmove.com</a> for assistance with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Property searches or listings.</li>
                <li>Inquiry submissions.</li>
                <li>Partnership opportunities.</li>
                <li>General questions or feedback about our platform.</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <p>Our dedicated support team is available to address your concerns promptly. Expect a response within 24-48 hours.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
